&lt;li&gt;Configure database environments, manage permissions, access control, and implement data governance frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement ELT processes using modern data stack tools such as Fivetran&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write high-quality code following Git workflows, code reviews, and CI/CD practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct data quality audits and implement automated testing frameworks&lt;/li&gt;
