&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced dbt proficiency with complex modeling, macros, and performance optimization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep Snowflake expertise including architecture, optimization, and advanced features&lt;/li&gt;
