&lt;li&gt;Understanding of dimensional modeling and analytics engineering methodologies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud environments and scalable solutions in AWS and/or GCP&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with project management tools like Jira&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI &amp;amp; Innovation Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
